# Script Name   : curl.sh
# Script version: 1.2
# Script date   : 2021-10-11
# Description   : CURL all sites. Write log into URL-specific log files
# Usage         : source ./curl.sh
# Author        : Toomas MÃ¶lder
# Email         : toomas.molder+curl@gmail.com
